#~ "I have brought many of my people along to aid us. My soldiers and shamans "
#~ "will now fight at your command."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "He traído a mucha de mi gente para ayudarnos. Mis soldados y chamanes "
#~ "lucharán a partir de ahora a vuestras órdenes."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Elvish Fighters are at home in thick forests. They have both a sword and "
#~ "a bow and are deadly with both. They are quick and can hold their own "
#~ "against just about anything."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Los luchadores elfos se encuentran como en casa en los bosques espesos. "
